   "source": [
    "# 词袋模型（Bag of Words）教程\n",
    "\n",
    "本Notebook将实现一个基础词袋模型，并用于计算文本相似度。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "081b9a13",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": []
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "71b66452",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1.导入依赖"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "60761b06",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from collections import Counter\n",
    "import re"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ae9605bf",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.文本分词（Tokenization）\n",
    "词袋模型的第一步是把文本变成“词”。这里做一个非常简化的版本：\n",
    "· 全部转小写。\n",
    "· 只保留英文和数字。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "6b194200",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def tokenize(text: str) -> list[str]:\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    简单分词：\n",
    "    1. 转小写\n",
    "    2. 只保留英文和数字\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    text = text.lower()\n",
    "    words = re.findall(r\"\\b[a-z0-9]+\\b\", text)\n",
    "    return words"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7f209b51",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "示例："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 12,
   "id": "bae6deff",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "['word2vec', 'is', 'useful']\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "print(tokenize(\"Word2vec is useful!!!!\"))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "da785ab9",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.构建词表（Vocabulary）\n",
    "\n",
    "词表 = 所有出现过的词的去重集合"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "id": "d2870f57",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def build_vocab(corpus: list[str]) -> list[str]:\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    构建词表（去重后排序）\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    vocab = set()\n",
    "\n",
    "    for sentence in corpus:\n",
    "        words = tokenize(sentence)\n",
    "        vocab.update(words)\n",
    "\n",
    "    return sorted(vocab)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "dfb70ce8",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 4.句子→词袋向量\n",
    "词袋模型的核心：<br>\n",
    "每个句子变成一个向量，向量的长度等于词表大小。  \n",
    "向量的每个位置表示该词出现的次数。   "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "id": "054ebf9b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def sentence_to_bow(sentence: str, vocab: list[str]) -> list[int]:\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    把一句话转成词袋向量\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    words = tokenize(sentence)\n",
    "    counter = Counter(words)\n",
    "\n",
    "    vector = []\n",
    "\n",
    "    for word in vocab:\n",
    "        vector.append(counter[word])\n",
    "\n",
    "    return vector"
   ]
  },
  {
