   "source": [
    "### 8.余弦相似度（Cosine Similarity）\n",
    "用余弦相似度来衡量两个句子的相似程度：\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\cos(\\theta) = \\frac{v_1 \\cdot v_2}{\\|v_1\\| \\, \\|v_2\\|}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "共享词越多→向量$v1$和$v2$的方向越相近→点积越大→相似度越高\n",
    "\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 18,
   "id": "40da1228",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import math\n",
    "\n",
    "def cosine_similarity(v1, v2):\n",
    "    dot = sum(a*b for a, b in zip(v1, v2))\n",
    "    norm1 = math.sqrt(sum(a*a for a in v1))\n",
    "    norm2 = math.sqrt(sum(a*a for a in v2))\n",
    "    return dot / (norm1 * norm2 + 1e-9)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f43b71d6",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 9.找最相似的句子"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 19,
   "id": "470a596c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def most_similar_sentence(query, corpus, vocab):\n",
    "    query_vec = sentence_to_bow(query, vocab)\n",
    "\n",
    "    best_sentence = None\n",
    "    best_score = -1\n",
    "\n",
    "    for sentence in corpus:\n",
    "        vec = sentence_to_bow(sentence, vocab)\n",
    "        score = cosine_similarity(query_vec, vec)\n",
    "\n",
    "        if score > best_score:\n",
    "            best_score = score\n",
    "            best_sentence = sentence\n",
    "\n",
    "    return best_sentence, best_score"
   ]
  },
